chivegrid/?p=1&q=rainer+fassbinder Various manuscript items] are held at a number of repositories\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n* [http://www.fassbinderfoundation.de Fassbinder Foundation] {{in lang|de}}\n* {{IMDb name|1202}}\n* [http://jclarkmedia.com/fassbinder/index.html#introduction Overview of Fassbinder's cinematic and theatre careers]\n* [http://www.lib.berkeley.edu/MRC/Germanfilmbib.html#Fassbinder Fassbinder Bibliography (via UC Berkeley)]\n* [http://www.villagevoice.com/film/0309,sontag,42133,20.html Interview with Hanna Schygulla about Fassbinder]\n* {{YouTube|zDjyxgerif4|Short film clip with Fassbinder's editor Julianne Lorenz}}\n* [http://www.filmdenken.de/essay/fassbinder.htm Essay on Fassbinder's Films] {{in lang|de}}\n* [http://www.goethe.de/kue/flm/far/en6013539.htm \"We still miss him\"], Goethe Institut article, May 2010\n* [http://www.peterlind.org/o/#Der_M\u00fcll,_die_Stadt_und_der_Tod ''Garbage, the City, and Death''], Copenhagen 1987, photostream by [[Peter Lind]] featuring photos of Fassbinder\n* {{Find a Grave|7918599}}\n\n{{Rainer Werner Fassbinder}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Fassbinder, Rainer Werner}}\n[[Category:1945 births]]\n[[Category:1982 deaths]]\n[[Category:20th-century German dramatists and playwrights]]\n[[Category:20th-century German male actors]]\n[[Category:Barbiturates-related deaths]]\n[[Category:Directors of Golden Bear winners]]\n[[Category:Best Director German Film Award winners]]\n[[Category:Bisexual male actors]]\n[[Category:Bisexual writers]]\n[[Category:Cocaine-related deaths]]\n[[Category:Drug-related deaths in Germany]]\n[[Category:English-language film directors]]\n[[Category:German experimental filmmakers]]\n[[Category:German film directors]]\n[[Category:German-language film directors]]\n[[Category:German male dramatists and playwrights]]\n[[Category:German male film actors]]\n[[Category:German male television actors]]\n[[Category:German screenwriters]]\n[[Category:LGBT directors]]\n[