s.\n\n==Results==\n===Olympic Games===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n!Games\n!Round\n!Position\n!{{Tooltip|Pld|Games played}}\n!{{Tooltip|W|Won}}\n!{{Tooltip|D|Drawn}}\n!{{Tooltip|L|Lost}}\n!{{Tooltip|GF|Goals for}}\n!{{Tooltip|GA|Goals against}}\n!{{Tooltip|GD|Goal difference}}\n|-\n|align=left|{{flagicon|CAN}} [[Handball at the 1976 Summer Olympics|1976 Montreal]]\n|colspan=9|''Did not qualify''\n|-\n|align=left|{{flagicon|URS}} [[Handball at the 1980 Summer Olympics|1980 Moscow]]\n|colspan=9|''Did not qualify''\n|-\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Handball at the 1984 Summer Olympics|1984 Los Angeles]]\n|colspan=9|''Did not qualify''\n|-\n|align=left|{{flagicon|KOR}} [[Handball at the 1988 Summer Olympics|1988 Seoul]]\n|colspan=9|''Did not qualify''\n|-\n|align=left|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Handball at the 1992 Summer Olympics|1992 Barcelona]]\n|colspan=9|''Did not qualify''\n|-\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Handball at the 1996 Summer Olympics|1996 Atlanta]]\n|colspan=9|''Did not qualify''\n|-\n|align=left|{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Handball at the 2000 Summer Olympics|2000 Sydney]]\n|colspan=9|''Did not qualify''\n|-\n|align=left|{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Handball at the 2004 Summer Olympics|2004 Athens]]\n|colspan=9|''Did not qualify''\n|-\n|align=left|{{flagicon|CHN}} [[Handball at the 2008 Summer Olympics|2008 Beijing]]\n|Quarter-final\n|'''8th''' of 12\n|6\n|2\n|0\n|4\n|147\n|168\n| \u221221\n|-\n|align=left|{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Handball at the 2012 Summer Olympics|2012 London]]\n|Preliminary round\n|'''11th''' of 12\n|5\n|0\n|0\n|5\n|108\n|131\n| \u221223\n|-\n|align=left|{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Handball at the 2016 Summer Olympics|2016 Rio de Janeiro]]\n|Quarter-final\n|'''7th''' of 12\n|6\n|2\n|1\n|3\n|170\n|174\n| \u22124\n|-\n|align=left|{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Handball at the 2020 Summer Olympics|2020 Tokyo]]\n|colspan=9|''To be determined''\n|-\n!Total\n!3/11\n!0 Titles\n!17\n!4\n!1\n!12\n!425\n!473\n! \u201348\n|}\n\n===World Championship